---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../../components/CTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Roller Hearth Furnace Components For Continuous Loading" description="You deserve heavy-duty components that can handle continuous loading. Our specialized radiant tubes and roller fixings are designed for high-volume production.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-orange-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-4">Furnace Application Solutions</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-8 leading-tight">Roller Hearth Furnace Components For Continuous Loading</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 mb-12">
        <p>You deserve heavy-duty components that can handle the continuous loading and unloading requirements of your roller hearth furnace. Our specialized radiant tubes and roller fixings are designed to minimize mechanical failure and thermal distortion in high-volume production. You can achieve higher throughput and more consistent part quality in your continuous annealing or normalizing cycles by choosing our durable furnace consumables today.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Technical Challenge</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Roller hearth systems face extreme mechanical wear and heat loss. You need components that resist sagging and maintain thermal sealing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Weigu Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Weigu offers high-strength alloy radiant tubes and precision roller seals. You reduce maintenance downtime and improve thermal efficiency across the line.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Components For This Application</h2>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> High-Strength Radiant Tubes</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Precision Roller Seals</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Ceramic Fiber Lining</li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-orange-500">✔</span> Thermal Monitoring Systems</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <CTA title="Optimize Your Roller Hearth Process Today" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
